Cam::

She gently rocked her arms to calm the infant. "Shhh, baby. It's OK. 
We'll go back inside now."  She walked back inside and tried to 
comfort the child. She looked up at the ceiling. "Mom? Please tell me 
I wasn't this bad to take care of."  Never having delt with a child, 
she thought this whole experience was strange, but she was doing her 
best to take care of the little bot as best as she could.
